			<h1>HTML Demo</h1>

            <h2>Tables</h2>
            <table border="1">
            <table class="table table-bordered">
                <caption>Table 1: Sample Data</caption>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>First Name</th>
                        <th>Last Name</th>
                        <th>Email</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Data 1.1</td>
                        <td rowspan="2">Data 1.2 (Rowspan)</td>
                        <td>Data 1.3</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Data 2.1</td>
                        <td>Data 2.3</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="3">Data 3.1 (Colspan)</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
                <tfoot>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="3">Footer Content</td>
                    </tr>
                </tfoot>
            </table>

            <table class="table table-bordered">
                <caption>Table 2: More Sample Data</caption>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Column 1</th>
                        <th>Column 2</th>
                        <th>Column 3</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Item 1.1</td>
                        <td>Item 1.2</td>
                        <td rowspan="2">Item 1.3 (Rowspan)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Item 2.1</td>
                        <td>Item 2.2</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="2">Item 3.1 (Colspan)</td>
                        <td>Item 3.3</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
                <tfoot>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="3">Footer Information</td>
                    </tr>
                </tfoot>
            </table>

            <p>This section demonstrates the use of HTML tables with various elements such as <code>&lt;caption&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;thead&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;th&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;td&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>, and the attributes <code>rowspan</code> and <code>colspan</code>. Each table is styled using Bootstrap classes and contains sample data for illustration purposes.</p>
